item.title: CVE-2016-0205|2024-08-05T22:08:13.347Z -- ibm -- cloud%20orchestrator
item.description: A vulnerability has been identified in IBM Cloud Orchestrator 2.3, 2.3.0.1, 2.4, and 2.4.0.1 that could allow an attacker after authentication to enumerate valid users of the system. IBM X-Force ID: 109394.
